---
title: Caribbean Black Bean & Slaw Tacos with Charred Pineapple Chilli Salsa
description: Get ready to taco your taste buds on a tropical getaway! These Caribbean-inspired tacos are bursting with smokey beans, topped with a fiery-sweet charred pineapple chilli salsa that’s a flavour vacation in every bite. Zesty, colourful and totally irresistible - these tacos bring the sunshine to your plate!
